{
  "stem": "10181.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were, traditionally, religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're not Orthodox like the Hasidim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we used-- I think it was kosher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It probably was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then, later on, you couldn't keep kosher because the-- the-- it was forbidden.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The ritual slaughter was forbidden in Germany after Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I-- I don't think that-- by the time I remember well, I don't think it was kosher.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Couldn't have been because it wasn't-- you could no longer buy kosher meat or anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vaguely Passover.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember-- I also remember, vaguely, going to the synagogue, but I don't remember that well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we had-- we had in the town, an orphanage where I used to go to a lot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This orphanage, really, was a Jewish orphanage, which was run-- it was for the whole Rhineland, for the whole area.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was run by Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Leopold Rothschild, who was a well-known educator and very respected man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And even though I wasn't-- I was like a half an orphan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's not-- that's not the reason I went there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The reason was, it was a safe place to go to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a big house with-- with fence-- with a fence around it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It had a back to play.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could go and play there without being bothered by the-- by other kids.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember that in-- I used to go with my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Behind the house there was a park.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we used to-- he used to take me for a walk there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the older kids used to throw stones at us and call us dirty Jew, and-- and-- and the adults used to turn the other way or help them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it wasn't really a very nice place to go to anymore, the park.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
